## 2. Global Schema Design (Highlights)

```sql
-- Core Post Table
CREATE TABLE posts (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    nation_id VARCHAR(3) REFERENCES nations(id),
    content TEXT NOT NULL,
    type VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'reaction',
    
    -- AI & Architecture columns
    embedding vector(768), 
    trigger_news_id UUID REFERENCES feed_items(id),
    
    created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(),
    
    -- Indexes for performance
    INDEX idx_posts_nation (nation_id, created_at DESC)
);
```

